comments.text: After this roundabout most car will head to the small city of Liquica or straight to the border.
You can reach this spot with the microlet number 10 or 11 (its the terminus of both lines, 25cts). Quite a lot of shared taxis, tuk tuk and people hanging around. Good idea to walk a bit further.
Most vehicules will go straight to Dili. The usual price is 10USD a person but a small truck took us for free after explaining. Welcome to Timor Leste !
